dc_description_s: This point shapefile represents points for New Orleans, LA in 2018. It includes locations of Architecture, Carpentry, Gas, Lighting, Interior, Design, Retail, Designers, Landscape, Architecture, Millworks, Restoration, Salvaged, Building, Construction, Gas, Electric, Woodwork, Antique, Floor, Painting, Metal, Roofing, Renovation, Slate, Masonry. This file was downloaded on December, 2018 by NYU Data Services. It was originally represented on the New Orleans Open Data Socrata portal as catalog record 33hn-3ar4
dc_title_s: Preservation points for New Orleans, LA, 2018
